data:
{{version028}}
{{flavour|Summons one or more spiders.}}

'''Summon Spiders''' is a monsters-only spell that summons 1-<code><power>/80</code> spiders. Possible summons include<ref>{{source ref|0.28.0|spl-summoning.cc|3087}}</ref>:

*{{monsterlink|Redback}}
*{{monsterlink|Jumping spider}}
*{{monsterlink|Tarantella}}
*{{monsterlink|Culicivora}}
*{{monsterlink|Orb spider}}
*{{monsterlink|Wolf spider}}

Broodmothers can sustain at most five spiders summoned by this spell.

{{monsters with spell}}

==History==
*This spell was added in [[0.28]].

